OL,3,CFinance Minister to meet French
OL,4,Ccounterpart in Paris
OL,6,FTanaiste Simon Harris is to meet the
OL,7,FFrench Finance Minister and Secretary
OL,8,FGeneral of the Organisation for
OL,9,FEconomic Co-operation and Development
OL,10,F(OECD) in Paris.
OL,12,FMr Harris is travel to France as part
OL,13,Fof the Government's St Patrick's Day
OL,14,Fprogramme which is focused on trade
OL,15,Fpromotion and economic engagement with
OL,16,FEU partners.
