OL,3,CFinance Minister to meet French
OL,4,Ccounterpart in Paris
OL,6,FFollowing a meeting of EU finance
OL,7,Fministers on Tuesday morning in
OL,8,FBrussels, the Tanaiste will travel to
OL,9,FParis for a series of engagements in
OL,10,Fthe French capital.
OL,12,FA spokesman said the meetings are
OL,13,Flikely to "focus on the fallout from
OL,14,Fthe ongoing conflict in the Middle
OL,15,FEast" and the implications for the EU.
OL,17,FThis includes issues around oil supply
OL,18,Fwhich were discussed by the G7 on
OL,19,FMonday, the presidency of which is
OL,20,Fcurrently held by France.
