OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773111798
OL,3,CFinance Minister to meet French
OL,4,Ccounterpart in Paris
OL,6,FMr Harris's visit also comes ahead of
OL,7,FIreland assuming the Presidency of the
OL,8,FCouncil of the European Union later
OL,9,Fthis year, for which it anticipates
OL,10,FFrance will be a key partner.
OL,12,FHe will meet French Economy Minister
OL,13,FRoland Lescure and Secretary General
OL,14,Fof the OECD Mathias Cormann during the
OL,15,Ftwo-day visit.
